text: the crop is really good this season better than ever we've had an incredible year growing fields of cocoa leaves I'm proud to be helping these Latinos to make Coke from these leaves I become close friends with these workers and let me tell you I'm not building walls anymore we ship Coke straight to the USA where there's a huge demand especially in Washington the quality of our Coke is unmatched and it's no wonder we're getting so many orders the demand is only increasing and we are ready to deliver let's make America great again with this crop [Music]
